snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Seasonal Adventures – Luminous Night
snippet.description:
LUMINOUS NIGHT RELEASES APRIL 20, 2022! Viktor, Laura, and Tom shed some light on Luminous Night, the new Minecraft Dungeons Seasonal Adventure! Find out what inspired the glowing symbols, learn more about the new storage chest, and get to know the wildfire a.k.a Mob D from the first ever mob vote! If you don’t remember which mob won that vote, you obviously go to bed early in Minecraft or are the bravest player in the world. Luminous Night also bring lots of new pets and UI updates that are based on your feedback, so keep making yourselves heard! https://minecraft.net/dungeons

04:53 UI Updates
